      <title>全球股市抛售缓解，油价在三天暴跌后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于股指期货指向日本和美国基准价格反弹，且利比亚最大油田停产使人们的注意力重新集中在中东，油价在连续三天下跌之后出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
