    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数波动率创疫情以来新高，高于纳斯达克 100 指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/s-p-500-volatility-hits-highest-over-nasdaq-100-since-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一个充满罕见走势的一天中，标准普尔 500 指数期权波动率自新冠疫情爆发以来首次超过纳斯达克 100 指数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/s-p-500-volatility-hits-highest-over-nasdaq-100-since-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:03:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着抛售愈演愈烈，大型科技股交易员准备迎接更多波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/big-tech-traders-brace-for-more-swings-as-selloff-turns-violent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，投资者一直面临着一个两难的境地：是花大价钱购买市盈率高的科技巨头，还是等待更便宜的切入点并冒着错过今年最大牛市的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/big-tech-traders-brace-for-more-swings-as-selloff-turns-violent</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 22:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股市崩盘重创该国散户投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-market-wipeout-hammers-country-s-retail-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年大部分时间，日本股市都为散户投资者带来丰厚回报，不断创下新高，并扩大了散户的投资组合。但短短三天，情况就发生了变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-market-wipeout-hammers-country-s-retail-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疯狂星期一过后，交易员纷纷对冲极端市场事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/black-swan-hedging-breaks-out-on-wall-street-after-manic-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们纷纷为自己的投资组合投保，以防范极端的市场崩盘，这与疫情开始时的混乱时期如出一辙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/black-swan-hedging-breaks-out-on-wall-street-after-manic-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:55:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利称美国证券交易委员会正在寻求有关现金余额清扫的信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/morgan-stanley-says-sec-seeks-info-on-cash-balance-sweeps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利周一披露，美国证券交易委员会执法部门已要求提供有关“咨询账户现金余额被转移到关联银行存款计划”的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/morgan-stanley-says-sec-seeks-info-on-cash-balance-sweeps</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:41:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市崩盘导致标普 500 指数处于回调边缘：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近有关美国经济衰退的讨论 — — 大多数人认为为时过早 — — 引发了人们的警告，即今年的股市火爆上涨已经过度，全球市场再度出现动荡。]]></description>
